<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_0b5ab4a5-9531-498a-bb4f-624ecf3a8ba7" outputclass="ncc-clause"><meta><facet building="Class 1a"/><facet building="Class 1b"/><facet building="Class 2"/><facet building="Class 3"/><facet building="Class 4"/><facet building="Class 5"/><facet building="Class 6"/><facet building="Class 7a"/><facet building="Class 7b"/><facet building="Class 8"/><facet building="Class 9a"/><facet building="Class 9b"/><facet building="Class 9c"/><facet building="Class 10a"/><facet building="Class 10c"/></meta><sptc>13.7.8</sptc><title id="_861a154a-feea-4029-bd79-8527c23cfb69">Swimming pool heating and pumping</title><archive-num>2019: 3.12.5.7</archive-num><subclause id="_fb572fa4-6920-483f-8e1f-42ee2817884b" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_c3f73e35-e8aa-4334-9b49-f7af910074ed">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>Heating for a <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1487_0.7.0.xml#_4cbd9e00-0622-4dfd-9de4-913c80257732" id="_6db03100-1123-4a4a-86a5-69b31548aabc" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">swimming pool</xref> must be by—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_a01d550a-8942-4a59-b57a-2fb3f77d2c75">a solar heater not boosted by electric resistance heating; or</li><li id="_82b01ef8-b7fc-48ba-94f7-97b4777870a1">a heater using reclaimed energy; or</li><li id="_1641a591-e3a5-41ee-ac57-a11cb93cd8dd">a gas heater; or</li><li id="_66966f07-cf1c-443d-b972-e247f15d1eb4">a heat pump; or</li><li id="_80376e8f-a842-49c6-abbf-61ae77355635">a combination of (a) to (d).</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_e2020968-f293-40e9-80d4-1d33708ddd21" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_998ba7a9-15ca-48e4-861d-cd75ac16c583">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>Where some or all of the heating <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_d0f78ec5-216d-484e-b84f-ee8205dba34f" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> by (1) is by a gas heater or a heat pump, the <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1487_0.7.0.xml#_4cbd9e00-0622-4dfd-9de4-913c80257732" id="_32b0b8a7-2d7d-4e68-b052-32e85dac7019" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">swimming pool</xref> must have—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_7e437946-bc19-400c-8878-74d6d8b4affd">a cover with a minimum <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1420_0.4.0.xml#_e5acb40f-3d3d-4a3d-8987-f09f7eaadf77" id="_23cccd79-513d-426f-958e-2a93142a9473" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">R-Value</xref> of 0.05, unless located in a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1225_1.8.0.xml#_26276791-20ad-4404-951f-29b5bff0ff80" id="_c925a037-cded-4622-871b-ccca10caf097" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">conditioned space</xref>; and</li><li id="_d880d61b-2f5c-427a-b8fe-c18fd8487783">a time switch to control the operation of the heater.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_b3bdea8e-2d78-4532-a542-1ed042b0ead7" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_1ec409a0-738f-42b1-b752-d6fa82a183f3">SubClause</title><num>3</num><p>A time switch must be provided to control the operation of a circulation pump for a <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1487_0.7.0.xml#_4cbd9e00-0622-4dfd-9de4-913c80257732" id="_962a3391-5f46-46fa-aa0e-32da82fd3031" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">swimming pool</xref>.</p></subclause><subclause id="_1e172112-1619-4cb3-80c3-d7a307b07d9a" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_3d66ee75-3fce-4bfe-bde1-81939089a2bf">SubClause</title><num>4</num><p>For the purposes of 13.7.8, a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1487_0.7.0.xml#_4cbd9e00-0622-4dfd-9de4-913c80257732" id="_2fbd67d9-df28-4b56-b4a6-ea4edfc11d8e" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">swimming pool</xref> does not include a spa pool.</p></subclause></clause>